s://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Force_1x_AXS_RSV_BrickRed-Large-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Force_1x_AXS_RSV_BrickRed-Large-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Force_1x_AXS_RSV_BrickRed-Large-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Force_1x_AXS_RSV_BrickRed-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Apex_1x_BrickRed-Large.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Apex_1x_BrickRed-Large-800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Santa Cruz Stigmata\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Apex_1x_BrickRed-Large-800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Apex_1x_BrickRed-Large-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Apex_1x_BrickRed-Large-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Apex_1x_BrickRed-Large-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/MY24_Stigmata_CC_Apex_1x_BrickRed-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot-2023-08-01-at-9.21.50-AM.png\"><img width=\"1397\" height=\"754\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot-2023-08-01-at-9.21.50-AM.png\" alt=\"Santa Cruz Stigmata spec chart\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot-2023-08-01-at-9.21.50-AM.png 1397w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot-2023-08-01-at-9.21.50-AM-297x160.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot-2023-08-01-at-9.21.50-AM-800x432.png 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot-2023-08-01-at-9.21.50-AM-120x65.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Screenshot-2023-08-01-at-9.21.50-AM-768x415.png 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Available in five different builds and in one color, pricing starts at $4,299 with a rigid fork and rigid seatpost. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/en-US/bikes/stigmata\" target=\"_blank\">santacruzbicycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-santa-cruz-stigmata-gravel-bike-suspension-fork/\">New Santa Cruz Stigmata Gains Progressive Geo, Glovebox &amp; Suspension Compatibility</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"896f3aa45dcd471ce698693b5043ee8e8d55e38864c7edcd0775d9cd821b5dc1","category":"Cycling"}